Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算做味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么做的味噌汤  能把锅都做焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈他们说会晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做饭？姐姐你来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来打算这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你去处理下那个锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你好点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天没社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为临近考试所以早回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我怎么可能这种时间在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家的真不是时机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是逃避自己去做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边抱怨  一边按照妈妈他们说的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我误以为那就是所谓的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断忍耐  对父母所说的话言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为那就是成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我之前一直看你不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无顾虑地参加社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里想  为什么只有你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能随便做自己喜欢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈也总是任由你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么想他们都是比较疼你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过是因为指望不了  所以对我听之任之而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈总是只表扬你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是那个不爽的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承认我确实是她们引以为豪的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我已经决定不再扮演下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是高中生而已  却装作什么都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装作成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为世间就是如此  把一切都忍耐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这么做毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论后悔  还是失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会自己去一力承担
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想走自己要走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能坦率地说出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便被反对  也勇敢地说出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次我不会重蹈覆辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你要离开这个家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到寂寞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:08:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我听了你的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去听全国大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道姐姐你真要来看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等妈妈回来之后叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前我睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让自己后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也没有社团活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早回那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车内请使用静音模式  不要接听电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了你烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有CD吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吹的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  想吹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和姐姐一起吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也感到寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师也说让夏纪出场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而夏纪也同意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今老调重弹是要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川同学和我说  其实她是希望你来吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然那么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下  会有人很直白地说自己想吹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把精力集中在考试上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始不就说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  给你们一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这题解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她要说那种谎话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很想去全国大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很想吹奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是高中生而已  却装作什么都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装作成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…所以我想走自己要走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能坦率地说出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便被反对  也勇敢地说出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  高一的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  明日香学姐在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是吹奏部的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我的教室  你肯定很紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是别人送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些话一定要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非终于要对我进行爱的告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我家一起独处的时候暗生情愫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出席竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我的回答是NO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由是  我不参加对社团来说更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个练习也不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛能不能出场都不知道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换作是我  绝对不想她参加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有原因的人多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我之前还反对过希美回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在自己遇到这事就特殊对待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话能说出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  大家都在说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望明日香学姐出席比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说你敢保证大家说的都是真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「明日香学姐出席比赛比较好」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「想和明日香学姐一起吹奏」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家当然会这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那样说不会有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会被别人指责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此  也不一定所有人都是那么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我们低音组  夏纪学姐都是希望你能出席比赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你能如此肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是能肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前竟然会说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我很好奇你有你说的那么了解他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在霙和希美的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后也只是在一旁观望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划清界线  绝对不深入一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明处于好奇去接近了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却害怕自己和别人受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择妥协  在安全的地方进行观望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得对于这样的人  对方会说出真心话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为你难得这么有气势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就没电了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这样淡出是最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心  大家不久就会忘记我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后同心协力去面对比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正结束之后  不管如何三年生都要引退的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是看不出她是这样的人
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}选择对这个部来说最好的\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}我希望你能替我们转告明日香学姐\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我的感觉是那种只要自己能吹奏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让自己后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是社团的事  还是竞赛会的事你都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和明日香学姐一起出席比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说这种孩子气的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子气有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你才是  为什么要扮成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表现得什么都懂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得只有自己是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你也只是一个高中生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做哪里是最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  你不是很想让你的父亲听到你演奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是比任何人都更想去全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能把这一切都当作不存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得只要忍耐  只要放弃就能让一切变好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是你的自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了我们在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要去选择那条一定会后悔的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放弃也要拼尽全力到最后才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望明日香学姐能站上全国大赛的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在那个音乐厅和学姐一起吹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要听学姐演奏的悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸都大花猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道会这样  不说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看看你的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢看我会诅咒你世世代代的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  久美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了明日香  池田老师在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是关于之前的模拟考  有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟考…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  高坂同学又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是升学班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是提前回家复习去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来一直都没和她说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人送了我妈一些点心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来给你们家一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子姐大学不念了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  5分钟后开始练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  难道你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐也真是坏心眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  是明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说明日香学姐模拟考的成绩进了全国前30名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她用这个和她妈妈进行了交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说自己无论如何都想比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用和我道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在等明日香学姐你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
